The evidence with the title 'Obama: when Reagan was governor of California, the Smog Was ... ' says Jan 18, 2016  ... Obama attended Occidental College in California from 1979 to 1981 before transferring to Columbia University in New York . In 1979  ... When Ronald Reagan was governor in California , there were regularly days where the smog was so bad, it was like it is in Beijing now. People just wouldn't go outside. 
